m in the \"Strong\" starting tier. Both **Marcell Ozuna** (63.3) and **Andy Pages** (59.1) also carry the \"Rain Risk\" warning, though their scores keep them in the lineup for now. **Heliot Ramos** presents a marginal play with a 42.6 score, facing a tougher opponent in Rhett Lowder (3.31 SP_xERA), and would be one of the first to be reconsidered if weather or lineup changes shift opportunities.",
